      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islip%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The town grew from a Native American settlement into a maritime and tourism hub after 1683.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        7
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
