      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islip%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "By 1950 Islip’s population was 71,000 and it exploded to 280,000 by 1970, turning the town into a major Long Island suburb.",
